title: Reincarnated As a Fish
summary: Reincarnated As a Fish ManhwaOn the verge of death from the betrayal of his trusted colleague, ‘Lee Yoo Shin’ sees a ray of light moments before dying. “Do you want to start a new life again?” When he came to his senses, there was a vast reservoir in front of him and his body had turned into a fish. Will he be able to overcome all the hardships and return to his family’s arms? 물고기로 살아남기 물고기로 살아남기!
